Ask to borrow my scarf, Corinne.
I did not take your scarf.

19:59.120 --> 20:00.952
I always lend you
my things, don't I?

20:01.160 --> 20:03.197
Last week I lent you
my black pantsuit, didn't I?

20:03.400 --> 20:07.474
Of course, it came back
with an entire leg missing,
but did I complain?

20:07.720 --> 20:10.633
You want your scarf?
Take a look over there.

20:10.840 --> 20:13.150
You thieving little fruit!

20:13.360 --> 20:15.716
Hey, wait a minute.

20:18.280 --> 20:19.953
My brother is not a fruit.

20:20.160 --> 20:23.153
He's a practical joker
with a wonderful
sense of humour.

20:23.360 --> 20:26.000
Danny, put her down.
She's a girl.

20:26.200 --> 20:29.318
Children, children,
now, let's not squabble.

20:29.520 --> 20:31.079
Stop it.
We're a family.

20:31.280 --> 20:34.671
Yes, that's right,
and a lovely family too.

20:38.880 --> 20:41.952
Now, come on,
everybody sit down, huh?

20:42.160 --> 20:47.679
Come on. Daddy,
I want us all to have
a nice time, hm?

20:49.680 --> 20:54.550
We're all going to
have some lovely
conversations.

20:59.800 --> 21:03.714
My son is coming after 15 years.
I'm gonna be with my so...

21:03.920 --> 21:07.231
We know, Burt, we know.
It's boring already.

21:13.240 --> 21:15.630
Aunt Jessica,
you look terrific tonight.

21:15.840 --> 21:20.153
No, no, I... I don't.
I... I don't look terrific at all.

21:20.360 --> 21:25.879
It's an allergy. I'm sick.
Yes, that's what it is.
I'm sick, sick.

21:31.000 --> 21:33.231
I'm considering getting
a sex-change operation.

21:35.320 --> 21:36.800
[LAUGHING]

21:37.000 --> 21:41.677
Would you listen to him?
What a sense of humour.

21:41.880 --> 21:44.076
He doesn't need an operation.
He could pass now.

21:45.520 --> 21:46.749
You take that back!

21:46.960 --> 21:48.872
Take your hands off my daughter!
Get your hands off him!

21:49.080 --> 21:50.080
[DOORBELL RINGS]

21:50.240 --> 21:53.597
Oh, my son.
My son! My son!

21:55.360 --> 21:57.591
